(Renjie Poker - App Summary) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 12 Tf 48 706 Td
(What It Is) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 48 692 Td
(Renjie Poker is a browser-based React game where the player builds a 5-card hand by selecting subsets from the remaining deck.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 48 678 Td
(The dealer receives all non-matching cards dealt during each turn; final hands are scored with poker rules and ties go to dealer.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 12 Tf 48 658 Td
(Who It Is For) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 60 644 Td
(- Primary persona \(explicit\): Not found in repo.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 60 630 Td
(- Likely user \(inferred from UI/rules\): players practicing probability and decision-making in a custom poker variant.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 12 Tf 48 610 Td
(What It Does) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 60 596 Td
(- Interactive card subset selection by suit, rank, select-all, and clear actions.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 60 582 Td
(- Deals one player card per turn when a selected card appears; dealer takes prior dealt cards in that turn.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 60 568 Td
(- Tracks remaining deck and disables cards already dealt.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 60 554 Td
(- Evaluates best poker hands for player and dealer, including straight/flush/full house/quads logic.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 60 540 Td
(- Completes showdown when player reaches 5 cards; dealer auto-tops to at least 8 cards.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 60 526 Td
(- Supports keyboard shortcuts for selection and game actions \(Enter, S/H/C/D, 2-9/T/J/Q/K/A, 0, X, N, ?\).) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10 Tf 60 512 Td
(- Includes theme toggle with localStorage persistence and a modal How to Play guide.) Tj
ET
